column6: To paid your Store acct with Mr Humpy Wallace
To Cash paid Mr Lewis for a Baby & 2 dozn Gun Flints
To Ferriages at Poseys, sendg to Mr Chapmans forye
To Cash sent you to pay for ye [the] Publishg an answer to ye [the] 10th Centinal which was never p'd
To the Printg Office, chargd in my Acct for Advertiseing a Runaway Negroe
To Cash lent Mrs Ann Washington (his Widow)
To Do paid Mr Chs Digges's Acct for his Estate
To Cash paid for 2 1/2 yds Swanskin @ 2/6
To Do pd for 1 Black Jack
To 1 Quartr Cask of Lisbon Wine of Adam
To 3 pr stone Earings of Mr Craig @ 22/6
To 2 Spinning Wheels of James Wren @ 16/
By Cash in Williamsburg £6 Ditto in Ditto £3
By Balle (no allowance for Feathrs) due GW
By the above Feathers viz 125 1/2 lbs @ 1/3
By Balle due G. W.—n & chd pr Contra
By Cash recd of Mrs Ann Washington pr my Br. John Washington
